A 23-year-old man was shot dead by a group of gunmen who were driving a Nissan Tiida. CAPE TOWN -  A 23-year-old man was killed and four wounded on the corner of Military Road and Prince George Drive in Steenberg on Tuesday morning. The police's Andre Traut  said: “Four other male persons aged 19, 20, 30 and 78 were shot and wounded during the same incident. Suspects in a Nissan Tiida open fire on the victims.” (Edited by Mihlali Ntsabo)